h1. p:siteURL

h2. Purpose

Renders an absolute URL pointing to the site. This is a shortcut for using g:createLink with absolute="true".

See [siteLink|tagsUiExtension] for details of the site link tag that uses this and @p:siteName@.

h2. Example

{code:xml}
<p:siteURL/>
{code}

h2. Attributes

None

